  "feedback": "The tests in `src/readme.test.ts` are well-structured, comprehensive, and correctly validate the required README changes. They cover both checklist item 13 and the new `## Search` section, verifying presence, position, and key content. The regex patterns are appropriately scoped and case-insensitive, ensuring robustness. No issues found.",
